https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oEMyf4DuSjXT6glQXIexD4yIPSs.jpg BIG PLANS follows the petty and irresponsible crook Willy, who has a massive fondness for music. Though he's 38 years of age he will not give up his lifelong dream of becoming a famous musician. When he gets paroled he therefore decides to revive his old band to prove to his eight-year-old son, Mikkel, that he isn't the failure everyone thinks he is. Big Plans!
